{
  "doc_id": "164",
  "text": ". For the determination of urease activity, the modified procedure was adopted according to the description [CITATION_1] . Briefly, 5 g fresh soil was incubated with 2.5 mL 0.08 M urea solution and 20 mL borate buffer (pH 10.0) for 2 h at 37uC. Released ammonium was extracted using 50 mL 2 M KCl solution, and determined colorimetrically at 690 nm.",
